<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٧٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٦٠٢٨ - يَزِيدُ أَبُو شَيْبَةَ، عَنِ الْحَكَمِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَوَّلُ مَنْ عَرَّفَ بِالْكُوفَةِ ابْنُ الزُّبَيْرِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>